data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom bungalow, nestled in a serene neighborhood of South Euclid. The living room boasts abundant natural light streaming through large windows. The nicely sized eat in kitchen features modern appliances, and ample counter space Off the kitchen is the family room that has a fireplace and sliding glass doors leading to the back yard. Venturing further, you'll discover two generously sized bedrooms. Upstairs you will find a large third bedroom. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home!
